    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sound E46 M3, a pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering. At its heart is the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system that has been recently serviced for optimal cam timing. Power is delivered via a precise Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox to a limited-slip rear differential. The chassis remains taut, with a reinforced rear subframe and refreshed bushings to maintain the original kinematics. This car exhibits a visceral 8,000 RPM redline and exceptional throttle response. While the exterior shows minor signs of road use, the drivetrain and suspension are dialed in for the serious driver seeking authentic M-division performance.",
